metadata.name: Hidden
metadata.description: The Spiritual Kitty is a collection of unique funny kitties living on Polygon Blockchain. Each kitty is one of a kind and 100% owned by you; it cannot be replicated, taken away, or destroyed. Holding a kitty grants you access to future members-only perks and features. Your NFT metadata is hosted on the IPFS the distributed web with a unique CID. We are also working with Pinata as a pinning tool to assure that your NFT Metadata will be on IPFS forever and no risk to lose it.
